# Release notes: Insight AnalytiX v2.1.0 (GA)

**Release Date:** March 24, 2022 
**Build Number:** 2.1.0.442  
**Deployment Type:** General Availability (GA)

## Overview
Insight AnalytiX v2.1.0 introduces enhanced data discovery capabilities and streamlined node management. This release focuses on improving scan performance for large-scale storage environments and expanding support for cloud-native protocols.

---

## New features
* **Multi-threaded scanning:** Improved scan efficiency by 30% for high-density file systems through optimized DITA-based modular indexing[cite: 10, 22].
* **Astro Starlight integration:** Launched a new web-based documentation portal using the Docs-as-Code methodology for real-time technical updates.
* **Webhooks for real-time alerts:** Added support for outbound webhooks, allowing integration with third-party collaboration tools for instant scan notifications[cite: 13].

---

